title: MasterChef.The.Professionals.S07E02.PDTVx264.mp4
description: The second heat sees five more chefs enter the kitchen, with the first challenge giving them an hour to cook a plate of food that showcases what they can do, before one is asked to leave. The remaining four contenders try to impress Monica Galetti and Gregg Wallace with their pasta skills, while Marcus Wareing gives them just 10 minutes to rustle up a pineapple dish and 60 minutes to cook a meal of their own choosing. Marcus and Monica then decide which three make it through to the next round
